{"tid":1662565,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"小島秀夫隻新Game首主題曲，其實就係講緊香港人...","createTime":"2019-10-19T00:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T14:57:03.000Z","uid":119173,"like":11,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"826d655b2f249d76b71eeb0f2440d66f75bb1b02","tid":1662565,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:16:37.000Z","msg":"遊戲界著名監制小島秀夫 (Hideo Kojima) 以Metal Gear Solid 系列成名，自從2015年脫離日本遊戲廠商 Konami後，將會係11月8日推出首隻以「小島秀夫」自己名義既遊戲 Death Stranding <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（「小島秀夫vs Konami」呢個故事本身都排講，大家可以自己google下）<br />\n<br />\n而 Death Stranding 呢隻遊戲挾住 「Kojima親生仔」之名，一直於全球不同大小遊戲展都成為眾人追訪對象。<br />\n<br />\nDeath Stranding 主題曲：<br />\nCHVRCHES - Death Stranding<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mFGq92BYmt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmFGq92BYmt4&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9hn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=90733bcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mFGq92BYmt4</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n（我試下釋一段仔個chorus俾大家）<br />\nLet's make a toast to the damned waitin' for tomorrow<br />\nWhen we're played out by the band drowning out our sorrows<br />\nWhat will become of us now at the end of time?<br />\nWe'll be fine, you and I<br />\nLet's draw a line in the sand, keep it straight and narrow<br />\nWe had it all in our hands, we begged and then we borrowed<br />\nWhat will become of us all at the end of love<br />\nWhen we've stopped looking up?<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">You can take my heart （你可以奪走我的心臟）<br />\nAnd hold it together as we fall apart （在倒下之時我們還會團結一致）<br />\nMaybe together we can make a mark in the stars we embark （彼此的經歷會在星空中留下記號）<br />\nAnd keep us together as the lights go dark （讓我們在漆黑中繼續閃燦）</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\nLet's tell the truth, just for once, asking for an answer<br />\nNow that it's all said and done, nothing really matters<br />\nWhat will become of us all if we dare to dream<br />\nAt the end of the scene?<br />\n<br />\nYou can take my heart<br />\nHold it together as we fall apart<br />\nMaybe together we can make a mark in the stars we embark<br />\nAnd keep us together as the lights go dark<br />\n<br />\nLet's open up to the sky, askin' it for closure<br />\n'Least we can say that we tried, but it's never really over<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>What will become of us all at the end of the line?<br />\nWill we live? Will we die?</strong></span> （煲底之約<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nYou can take my heart<br />\nAnd hold it together as we fall apart<br />\nMaybe together we can make a mark in the stars we embark<br />\nAnd keep us together as the lights go dark<br />\nAnd you can take my heart<br />\nAnd hold it together as we fall apart<br />\nMaybe together we can make a mark in the stars we embark<br />\nAnd keep us together as the lights go dark<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重點：<br />\nDeath Stranding 將會於11月8日推出，肯定成為全球 gamer 關注既盛事。大家上 YouTube search &ldquo;death stranding&rdquo; 就知受歡迎程度有幾勁，當中既同名主題曲亦會必然申理成章成為熱門搜尋項目。<br />\n<br />\n主題曲既詞，形容緊既正正就係香港人既團結力量。當中 &ldquo;What will become of us all at the end of the line? Will we live? Will we die?&rdquo; 簡直就係描寫緊大家煲底下的約定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。請各界高手幫推，一齊以 Death Stranding 既曲詞加入香港時代革命既歷史片段，等外國媒體一齊關注事件，實行 #weconnect <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"24098967d54e9c7a5b357777e189552cd354ef81","tid":1662565,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:22:17.000Z","msg":"晨早推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2c9941b409b131ef744a7cb511a5c95d90ce98","tid":1662565,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d2e8e10c4c35fb48c4cfb0931f238e7397162d","tid":